Compute the natural logarithm of the number.



```js
ln(num: number) -> number
```

### Tags

* `math`


### Arguments

| Name | Type | Description | Required |
|----------|------|-------------|----------|
| `num` | `number` |  | Yes |

### Returns

`number` 


### Examples

```js
const exampleSketch = startSketchOn("XZ")
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([ln(100), 15], %)
  |> line([5, -6], %)
  |> line([-10, -10], %)
  |> close(%)

const example = extrude(5, exampleSketch)
```
